These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: cola, juice, lemonade, water
Music-Genre: house, blues, funk, indie
1. Beverage:cola is on the right of Music-Genre:funk##1
2. Music-Genre:indie is on the far left##1
3. Music-Genre:funk is between Music-Genre:blues and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:water is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:lemonade is between Beverage:juice and Beverage:cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Music-Genre      | indie | house | funk   | blues |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Job: electrician, teacher, paramedic, firefighter
Nationality: british, colombian, dutch, turkish
1. Nationality:turkish is between Job:paramedic and Nationality:colombian##2
2. Job:firefighter is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:dutch is on the right of Nationality:british##1
4. Job:electrician is on the left of Nationality:british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Job         | teacher | electrician | paramedic | firefighter |
| Nationality   | colombian    | turkish   | british | dutch       |

