.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Food: cauliflower, corn, cranberry, kale
Music-Genre: classical, folk, rock, reggae
1. Music-Genre:rock is on the right of Food:kale##1
2. Music-Genre:rock is between Music-Genre:folk and Food:corn##2
3. Music-Genre:folk is on the far left##1
4. Music-Genre:reggae is on the left of Food:cranberry##1
5. Food:corn == Music-Genre:reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| Music-Genre   | folk | rock   | reggae | classical |

